OBJECT Report 35 Document Entries
{
  OBJECT-PROPERTIES
  {
    Date=14/08/09;
    Time=12:00:00;
    Version List=NAVW16.00.01;
  }
  PROPERTIES
  {
    CaptionML=[ENU=Document Entries;
               ESP=Listas de documentos];

  DATAITEMS
  {
    { PROPERTIES
      {
        DataItemTable=Table2000000026;
        DataItemTableView=SORTING(Number)
                          WHERE(Number=FILTER(1..));
        OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                        IF NOT PrintAmountsInLCY THEN
                          CurrencyCaption := Text003
                        ELSE
                          CurrencyCaption := '';
                      END;

        OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                           IF Number = 1 THEN BEGIN
                             IF NOT DocEntry.FIND('-') THEN
                               CurrReport.BREAK;
                           END ELSE
                             IF DocEntry.NEXT = 0 THEN
                               CurrReport.BREAK;

                           IF ISSERVICETIER THEN
                             CurrencyCaptionRBC := Text003;
                         END;

      }
      SECTIONS

    { PROPERTIES
      {
        DataItemIndent=1;
        DataItemTable=Table112;
        DataItemTableView=SORTING(No.);
        OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                        IF DocEntry."Table ID" <> DATABASE::"Sales Invoice Header" THEN
                          CurrReport.BREAK;

                        SETCURRENTKEY("No.");
                        SETFILTER("No.",DocNoFilter);
                        SETFILTER("Posting Date",PostingDateFilter);
                      END;

        OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                           IF PrintAmountsInLCY THEN BEGIN
                             IF "Currency Code" <> '' THEN BEGIN
                               Amount := CurrExchRate.ExchangeAmtFCYToLCY("Posting Date","Currency Code",Amount,"Currency Factor");
                               "Amount Including VAT" := CurrExchRate.ExchangeAmtFCYToLCY("Posting Date","Currency Code",
                                                         "Amount Including VAT","Currency Factor");
                             END;
                           END;
                         END;

      }

    { PROPERTIES
      {
        DataItemIndent=1;
        DataItemTable=Table114;
        DataItemTableView=SORTING(No.);
        OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                        IF DocEntry."Table ID" <> DATABASE::"Sales Cr.Memo Header" THEN
                          CurrReport.BREAK;

                        SETCURRENTKEY("No.");
                        SETFILTER("No.",DocNoFilter);
                        SETFILTER("Posting Date",PostingDateFilter);
                      END;

        OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                           IF PrintAmountsInLCY THEN BEGIN
                             IF "Currency Code" <> '' THEN BEGIN
                               Amount := CurrExchRate.ExchangeAmtFCYToLCY("Posting Date","Currency Code",Amount,"Currency Factor");
                               "Amount Including VAT" := CurrExchRate.ExchangeAmtFCYToLCY("Posting Date","Currency Code",
                                                         "Amount Including VAT","Currency Factor");
                             END;
                           END;

                        SETRANGE(Status,"Production Order".Status::Released,"Production Order".Status::Finished);
                        SETFILTER("No.",DocNoFilter);
                      END;

    PROCEDURE TransferDocEntries@1(VAR NewDocEntry@1000 : Record 265);
    VAR
      TempDocumentEntry@1001 : Record 265;
    BEGIN
      TempDocumentEntry := NewDocEntry;
      NewDocEntry.RESET;
      IF NewDocEntry.FIND('-') THEN
        REPEAT
          DocEntry := NewDocEntry;
          DocEntry.INSERT;
        UNTIL NewDocEntry.NEXT = 0;
      NewDocEntry := TempDocumentEntry;
    END;

    PROCEDURE TransferFilters@4(NewDocNoFilter@1000 : Code[250];NewPostingDateFilter@1001 : Text[250]);
    BEGIN
      DocNoFilter := NewDocNoFilter;
      PostingDateFilter := NewPostingDateFilter;
    END;

    BEGIN
    END.
  }

  <Code>Public Function BlankZero(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value = 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankPos(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &gt; 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankZeroAndPos(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &gt;= 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankNeg(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &lt; 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankNegAndZero(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &lt;= 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function
</Code>
